Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:10.37,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Sunraku-san... still hasn't returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:21.54,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Which means... he's still fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.26,Default,Emul,0,0,0,,Sunraku-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.10,0:02:04.98,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I guess we'll need more than stat \Nboosts to make a breakthrough here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.23,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Its armor seems thickest around the waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.69,0:02:11.49,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,That's probably where all the \Nimportant bits are stored...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:16.74,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,But how the heck do we \Ngo about prying it open?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:20.83,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\an8}I've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:21.87,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:22.75,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,An idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:26.17,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,A surefire plan to break through \NKirin Armor's outer shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:27.88,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I call it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.13,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.68,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,That which can cleave even dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.68,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.19,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the heck was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.24,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Sky Clear", he called it, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this move is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:01.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}way too nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:08.13,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Will it reach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:08.88,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:19.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's like I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:25.18,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's gonna take more than that to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:36.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,My ultimate technique, the self-revive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was a huge gamble, but I managed to \Ntime it just right to revive myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:41.83,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, my equipment's not so lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:44.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Spiked Battlehelm is half trashed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:47.12,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Lifestide Sash is totally kaput.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:50.21,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That "Clear Sky" move
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:51.63,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}is nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.26,0:03:59.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}So it's got equipment-destroying \Nand armor-piercing effects...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.97,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe the Insta-Death effect, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.06,0:04:04.35,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:08.44,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Until you surpass my ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:11.23,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,I shall not fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:14.03,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That stance again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.32,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.94,0:04:18.03,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:21.03,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hang on a damn minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're back to the attack spam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.71,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.12,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.04,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:33.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too damn close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.09,0:04:36.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.30,0:04:39.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That chain of attacks and \Nthe final Sky Clear move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of it together makes \Nup "Clear Sky Conquest."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:46.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}So... how do I solve it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:51.48,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last time, it took about thirty \Nseconds before the Sky Clear hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:52.31,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Pyroclastic Wyrm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.73,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's lag time before \NPyroclastic Wyrm activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:58.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That one's not a huge threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:01.41,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Ash Blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.58,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same with Ash Blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:08.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's easy to dodge when I know it's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:10.50,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal Rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.79,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The moves he uses in Clear Sky \NConquest might be chosen at random,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.42,0:05:17.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}but the actual dodging \Nis a memorization game!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.97,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Given all the moves in his arsenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:23.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}the go-to strategy is to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.47,0:05:26.93,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}preserve stamina and keep about \Nthree meters from him at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:28.64,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Keep your movements to the bare minimum.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't so scary once you get used to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}He got my leg again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's thirty seconds, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:44.66,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now, here's the real challenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.08,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.33,0:05:50.50,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's killed me plenty of times before, \Nbut this one feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's more fundamentally...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:57.71,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}an insta-kill attack, meant to slaughter \Nthe player without you getting a say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:06.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll bet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:11.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if a level 99 player buffed \Ntheir defenses with full armor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:12.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a shield at the ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:16.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}he'd still split them in \Nhalf like a block of tofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.19,0:06:19.82,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Until you surpass my ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:23.28,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,I shall not fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:25.91,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:35.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the worst part of all is \Nthat he keeps you from dodging!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once you're rooted to the spot like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.05,0:06:41.55,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}you don't have a choice but \Nto soak his Sky Clear attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.84,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.72,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Destroy his sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:52.64,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that's not a realistic option when \Nyou're dodging the attack spam...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.44,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same with taking down the guy himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.98,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was my last Rebirth Tearjewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.74,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}All I've got left are five Divine Lifesalves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:07.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If the Sky Clear comes every thirty seconds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.87,0:07:10.41,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}that means I've got three \Nminutes left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.75,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been less than five \Nminutes since Phase 3 started.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't make it to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.04,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Until you surpass my ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:20.50,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,I shall not fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:24.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until I "surpass" it... he won't fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.59,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:29.51,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.27,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Thunderclap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.19,0:07:40.27,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}But then, the "survive ten minutes" \Nthing was just a theory from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:46.11,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I'm thinking "survive the Clear \NSky Conquest" is a more likely scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.24,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:58.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Solving the Sky Clear must be the \Nvictory condition against Wethermon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:03.30,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the key to doing that \Nhas gotta be to parry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Against an opponent of Wethermon's caliber,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:09.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'd need to deflect with \Nthe timing of a critical...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.26,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've gotta do it while rooted to one spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:15.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}in a state where you can't \Nmake any stance adjustments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:19.31,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get the timing off by a millisecond, \Nhe'll shatter your weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, it's the only way to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:26.86,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}My job right now is to work out \Nwhat I need in that final moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.86,0:08:30.07,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}and make sure I have it at my disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:34.70,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.58,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon, I'll have everything I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:39.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait just a little while longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:40.88,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wethermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:44.21,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Until you surpass my ultimate,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:46.80,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,I shall not fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:02.23,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Let Sunraku-kun handle all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:06.69,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Yeah, we've got our own job to focus on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.69,0:09:12.36,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Now, as far as your surefire way \Nto take down Kirin Armor goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:16.12,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,It's not gonna be easy to \Nget him where we need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.62,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Can't do it, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.62,0:09:19.08,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.08,0:09:21.62,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Don't go underestimating a fighting game pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.83,0:09:23.00,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:24.92,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Get on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.13,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Wh-Why'd you just kill yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.36,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That took forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:49.65,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.03,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,H-Hey, that's my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:55.99,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,A spear-wielder can't \Nfight with just one hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.99,0:09:58.12,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,But resurrection sets me back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:00.33,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,At least warn me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.83,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Now, let's start again fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:06.75,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}First, gotta find its weak spot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:12.01,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}The backbone linking the \Ntop and bottom portions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:14.22,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}It feels just like the other parts!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:16.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! I'm right over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.89,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Not as easy to shake off this time, am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.60,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I've drugged myself into a major buff stack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.98,0:10:26.23,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and{\i0} I'm using two whips!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.86,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,The second you lift up \Nthe leg, the body falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:36.41,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo-kun, well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:39.08,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,If you wanna be a fighting \Ngame pro in the VR game age,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:45.92,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,you'd better know how the human body \Nmoves under any set of circumstances!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:47.59,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,This thing isn't really human!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.88,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,It's humanoid! Basically the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:55.18,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay, and that's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:10:59.85,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I add more whips!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.77,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I've got you wrapped up \Nin every whip I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:06.81,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I suppose that's the end of this weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:13.07,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adding armor-piercing buffs to your weapons \Nwears down their durability very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:18.82,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've hit its back, arms, and legs multiple \Ntimes over the course of the fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:21.29,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's just as tough all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:26.21,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still... there's one place where the \Narmor is tougher than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:29.71,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}That waist of yours is just too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.96,0:11:31.71,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo-kun! Move it forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.21,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.22,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I won't be able to hold it for long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:37.47,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:41.22,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's time to spill your guts, giant!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.14,0:11:43.97,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\an8}Spear of Sunlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.56,0:11:49.56,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Come on, you can hang in \Nthere a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.69,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,My buffs are about to run out, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.45,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I got it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.12,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Great! Then, let's finish the job!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:11.46,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,It shredded all my whips!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.97,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,The hell is this? A berserker mode?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.97,0:12:26.52,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Looks like breaking the \Nwaist armor set it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:28.23,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,What's the plan? Fall back for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.23,0:12:30.73,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,No, we press the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.73,0:12:32.40,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,If we just let it rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:37.24,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,one of those indiscriminate beams \Nor missiles might hit Sunraku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:41.20,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I think you can imagine \Nwhat that would lead to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:44.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.54,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,While I was going toe-to-toe \Nwith a unique monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:50.92,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}someone{\i0} couldn't even handle \Ndistracting his pet horse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:54.13,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'd sure love to hear {\i1}all{\i0} about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:59.93,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We'll be in for six months of {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:02.18,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,No doubt. I'd do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:03.39,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Yeah, so would I.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:05.06,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:08.77,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,In that case, we've done all our prep...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.40,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,So let's seal the deal \Non your surefire plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.77,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:15.73,Default,Pencilgon/Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Time for Giant Killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:27.54,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I only have two spears left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:30.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Boy, what a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.42,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Do you know how much it \Ncosts to make one of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:36.09,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Now's not the time to get stingy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.30,0:13:40.05,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Must be nice to just use your fists...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:42.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.39,0:13:46.06,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Thou art that which binds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:48.31,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I am that which holds fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:50.06,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I merge with all of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.23,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}I find the incompatible darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.94,0:13:55.06,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}and strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:04.74,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Shadow Wedge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:10.58,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Shadow Wedge...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:13.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's a spell that lets you \Nseal a target in place
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,by stabbing your weapon into its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:21.30,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It lasts until the weapon breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.55,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Given Kirin's size, that'll probably \Nbe about five seconds from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.35,0:14:28.10,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,We only get one chance at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.31,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Let's go... my last spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:36.06,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Giant Killing Skewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.32,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Perfect for a mammoth like \Nthis, don't you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.57,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's time, Katzo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:46.91,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Okay! Hold it tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.04,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Pencilgon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:52.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}Drat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,{\i1}It fired a missile before I locked it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:02.30,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.34,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,That's no problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:12.77,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I said that a spear-wielder \Ncan't fight with only one arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:15.19,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,but I take that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.44,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Kirin Armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:21.69,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,I only need one arm for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.48,0:15:26.49,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Go! Giant Killing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:32.08,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,All or Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.79,0:15:38.25,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,It's all yours, Katzo-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.09,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Red, Blue, Yellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.09,0:15:45.88,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Three colors merge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.72,0:15:49.47,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Spirit Fist: Dark Overstrike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:54.27,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Just go down already, you empty shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:59.61,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Human Pile Bunker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.23,0:16:05.03,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Katzo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.72,0:16:28.01,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I'm 'kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:45.48,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:47.78,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,We were so screwed if \Nthat hadn't clinched it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:52.53,Default,Oikatzo,0,0,0,,I'm so drained from Dark Overstrike \Nthat I can't move a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:54.16,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,You're out of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.16,0:16:55.79,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,Rest for a while and you'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:57.91,Default,Pencilgon,0,0,0,,How's Sunraku-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.34,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,That was my last resurrection item.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.05,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I made it in time, Wethermon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:15.68,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I've got everything I need now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.97,0:17:17.47,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Hungry Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:20.06,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Climax Boost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.56,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Their cooldowns are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.44,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And my Moonblades' fusion gauge is filled up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:32.03,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:35.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,In thirty seconds
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.74,0:17:38.00,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,you'll dish out your last Sky Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.08,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wethermon the Tombguard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.83,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I'm gonna solve your ultimate strike
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.84,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,and bring on the finale!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.46,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Wind Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.43,0:17:54.51,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Tidal Rush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:57.64,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Nimbus Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.27,0:18:05.90,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm using the cooldowns
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.65,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}to identify exactly how long his \NClear Sky Conquest has been going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.07,0:18:11.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sky Clear is coming in two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.16,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,It'll be your last Sky Clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.57,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Bring it on, Wethermon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:18.87,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key to beating it is the Moonblade...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.04,0:18:25.67,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Twin Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.00,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,The fusion of the blades \N"Waxing" and "Waning."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:30.92,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,It comes with a special effect:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:35.39,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,the lower your stats are, \Nrelative to your enemy's,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.81,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,the greater the power and \Nlikelihood of your criticals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.18,0:18:41.89,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the best weapon possible \Nfor these circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.52,0:18:45.15,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}It raises the likelihood \Nthat my parry will work!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.19,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:50.03,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}With the stacked effects of \NClimax Boost and Hunger Wolf,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.86,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll raise my action speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}With all this, I can block \Nhis Sky Clear for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:18:59.99,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,I can't activate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:06.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got a skill I can only activate \Nwhen my HP fall below one-third—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.25,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I screwed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.25,0:19:12.76,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}How'd I manage to blow my prep like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've soaked that attack \Nenough times to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:19.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hunger Wolf alone won't let \Nme match the attack speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.14,0:19:21.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think, man! There's gotta be a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:23.14,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sunraku, think!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.10,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Think up a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:25.77,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}You guys are all so obsessed \Nwith that Setsuna lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:49.17,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's major update changed \Nthe activation conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:51.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the luck-based "Endure" status...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.05,0:19:54.38,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}If your luck stat is over fifty,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.38,0:19:59.09,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}and your HP reaches zero due to \Nself-inflicted or recoil damage,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:03.43,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just once, you can hang \Nin there with a single HP!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:14.82,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Clear Sky Conquest is a chain of \Nactions that concludes with Sky Clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:20.53,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,In other words, until you release your \NSky Clear, you'll never give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:24.20,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Either on the Clear Sky Conquest action
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.79,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,or your oath to guard that \Ngrave forever and ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,On behalf of Vash, I'm putting you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:32.84,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Sky Clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:36.01,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Crescent Vorpal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:46.35,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Go to sleep already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:49.60,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,Wethermon the Tombguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.45,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,You were really strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.91,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,But I've seen enough of your \Nattacks for a lifetime...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:07.33,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,And your blade won't reach me ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.42,Default,Sunraku,0,0,0,,The ultimate strike has been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.68,0:21:24.93,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,Brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.81,0:21:31.94,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,You have broken through my ultimate strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.27,0:21:39.19,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,As "Clear Sky" transformed into \Nmy ultimate, "Sky Clear"...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:44.91,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,So, again, do the words transform... \Nto describe your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.63,0:21:59.55,Default,Wethermon,0,0,0,,"It is as clear as a cloudless sky."
